http://www.thehindu.com/news/cities/bangalore/Rowdy-sheeter-hacked-to-death/article13997314.ece

A 30-year-old rowdy-sheeter was hacked to death by a group of armed men in broad daylight in Hebbal on Wednesday. Tension gripped residents who witnessed Satish alias Gunda being chased and hacked to death. The attackers then fled the spot. Satish had multiple cases pending against him. The Hebbal police rushed to the spot and are conducting a probe.